    "title": [
      "[Hinterwilds, Stone Dragon]"
    ],
    "description": [
      "An enormous stone dragon slumbers amidst the woods, snow and underbrush encompassing much of its majestic shape.  Clusters of holly and white dryad have grown over the lifelike statue, blanketing it in incarnadine and niveous patches of flora.  Far more vivid, in jewel-bright colors, are the ice-slicked scales of the beast, a sea of blues and greens fading into burnished coppers.  Were it not perfectly still, it might be a living being."
    ],
